    "19(4), 42500 (2024) 1) Please note that this is by no means a standard or optimal choice that can be applied to every situation.",
    "The selection of the optimal discrete velocities depends not only on the discrete formats of time integral and spatial derivative, but also on the specific fluid behavior.",
